  "doc_id": "9833",
  "text": "Previous contributions on eICIC focus on performance gain brought about by this feature in a static heterogeneous network [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] , [CITATION_3] . In [CITATION_4] and [CITATION_5] , the eICIC parameters are optimized for a static scenario. The ABSr optimization problem has been treated for a dynamic environment in [CITATION_6] assuming fixed CIOs. The problem of optimizing both CIO and ABSr has been studied in [CITATION_7] , [CITATION_8] using a centralized approach. The solution is computationally demanding and can be implemented as a management plane solution.",
